### ==================================================
### 3. GET WORKER DETAILS (with services and portfolio)
### ==================================================

### Get Worker by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/workers/worker-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Workers (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workers?skip=0&take=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Verified Workers
GET {{baseUrl}}/workers/verified?skip=0&take=10
Content-Type: application/json

### ==================================================
### 4. PORTFOLIO MANAGEMENT
### ==================================================

### Add Portfolio Image
POST {{baseUrl}}/workers/{{workerId}}/portfolio
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/new-portfolio.jpg",
  "description": "Luxury bathroom renovation 2024"
}

### Get Portfolio Images
GET {{baseUrl}}/workers/{{workerId}}/portfolio
Content-Type: application/json

### Update Portfolio Image Description
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workers/{{workerId}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description - Professional plumbing work"
}

### Delete Portfolio Image
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workers/{{workerId}}/portfolio/{{portfolioId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ==================================================
### 5. UPDATE WORKER PROFILE
### ==================================================

### Update Worker Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workers/worker-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Ali Ahmed Khan Updated",
  "bio": "Updated bio - 6 years of experience",
  "experienceYears": 6,
  "visitingCharges": 600
}

